heading-order-3.title: Heading elements are not in a sequentially-descending order
heading-order-3.description: Properly ordered headings that do not skip levels convey the semantic structure of the page, making it easier to navigate and understand when using assistive technologies. [Learn more about heading order](https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.10/heading-order).

listitem-4.title: List items (`<li>`) are not contained within `<ul>`, `<ol>` or `<menu>` parent elements.
